TITLE: This Persian Noodle Soup Recipe Is The One-Pot Wonder You Need
SUMMARY: Rosh Hashanah doesn't always have to be about brisket and babka. Try ash-e-reshteh, an aromatic green soup swimming with noodles and beans.

TITLE: You Might Be Shocked By What Two Principals Said About My Transgender Daughter
SUMMARY: My breath stopped in my chest when Nicole's principal told her, "You are my greatest teacher."
